  python39-devel-3.9.16-1
  swig-4.4.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://sourceforge.net/projects/libhdate/

Canonical download:
  mirror://sourceforge/libhdate/libhdate-1.6.02.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libhdate-1.6.02-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libhdate-1.6.02-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libhdate-1.6.02-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libhdate-1.6.02-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libhdate1-1.6.02-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libhdate-devel-1.6.02-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/python39-hdate-1.6.02-X.tar.xz

